name: GuessMe
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: guess me
des: Guess Me is a fun guessing game where Alexa describes something and you have to guess who or what she is describing. Great for kids, but fun for anyone. Start by saying "Alexa, open Guess Me" and she will let you guide you through the game. You can say "help" at any time if you run into trouble and also tips on how to guess the answer. Remember that a parent needs to add permission in the Alexa app to use this skill! You should get a prompt upon your first invocation. I hope you have fun and enjoy playing.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
